# Playwright E2E artefacts (R-PORT-6) — never shipped with the image.
# The e2e specs themselves stay in the build context so the COPY tests
# step picks them up consistently with the rest of the test sources;
# Vite's bundle ignores them (no `import` from src/), and the
# devDependency footprint is unchanged for the production runtime.
